snippet.title: Judofuri - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Judofuri is a game I've been developing on my spare time for a few months, it's a silly party game with cute little fruits, where each player only needs one button to play. 

If you love couch gaming nights with friends and family, consider wishlisting the game on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3013460/Judofuri/
